location: National Cheng Kung University Fall Orchid Show, Taiwan

measurements.description: Two exceptional full, shapely flowers on one 21.3-cm erect inflorescence; sepals cream, heavily striped mahogany, dorsal sepal broad; petals cream, boldly spotted mahogany proximally, coalescing to stripes distally; pouch cream, blushed maroon; staminode cream, densely speckled maroon; substance very firm, texture glossy.
